# 5-Inch FPV Drone Build

## Overview

This build is based on a 5-inch Mark4-style freestyle frame and is equipped with 
reliable and budget-conscious components for solid performance in 
freestyle and general FPV flying.


---

## Components

### 🧱 Frame
- 5-Inch Freestyle Frame (Mark4 Copy)

### 🧠 Flight Controller & ESC Stack
- SpeedyBee F405 V3 Stack
  - F4 Flight Controller
  - 50A 4-in-1 BLHeli_S ESC
  - 30x30 mounting pattern

### ⚙️ Motors
- EMAX MT2204 II PLUS – 2300KV (x4)

### 📡 Receiver
- HappyModel EP1 RX
  - 2.4GHz ExpressLRS

### 📶 Video Transmitter (VTX)
- SpeedyBee TX800
  - Adjustable Power Output (up to 800mW)

### 📡 Antenna
- 80cm 5.8GHz Antenna

### 🪶 Propellers
- iFlight 5” Propellers

### 🎥 Camera
- 9IMOD 1800TVL FPV Camera
  - 5MP Sensor

### 🧭 GPS Module
- HGLRC M100
  - Supports GPS/GLONASS/QZSS



